\section{Conclusion}
In this letter, we proposed an undersampled method based on subspace techniques to estimate the frequencies of multiple sinusoids. Three sub-Nyquist sequences at specific sampling rates are shown to be general enough for the estimation from theoretical and experimental analysis. Through the numerical simulations, we verify that the method has enough robustness and accuracy.



























